Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,---------------------------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.96,0:00:07.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,倫 快一點 小透等著呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.40,0:00:09.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.17,0:00:12.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有忘東西吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.63,0:00:15.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.53,0:00:16.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,路上小心
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.06,0:00:19.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 我走了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.31,0:00:22.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久等咯
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.78,0:00:25.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好 小倫
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,---------------------------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.78,0:02:01.03,TITLE,+,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,0)\frz355.758\pos(410,628)}雨天就要泡澡{\fs40}-也像雨一樣-
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,---------------------------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.62,0:02:08.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒 這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.80,0:02:12.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊咧 昨天晚飯後我發過短信了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.57,0:02:15.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎？沒看到這樣的短信啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.57,0:02:18.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小倫
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.56,0:02:19.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.71,0:02:20.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的襪子
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.88,0:02:25.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊！另一隻忘穿了！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.39,0:02:29.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好丟人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.70,0:02:34.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣的話還不如光腳算了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.16,0:02:46.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小...小倫
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.58,0:02:48.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,內...內...內...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.23,0:02:50.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,內褲呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.09,0:03:01.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再怎麼說竟然會沒意識到 竟然會沒意識到...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.07,0:03:03.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能蹲下啊 能從前面看到的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.53,0:03:07.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為睡得太死了？ 就因為這點理由？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.34,0:03:11.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會有這種事 該怎麼辦啊...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.34,0:03:11.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事的 誰都有忘東西的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.11,0:03:14.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然忘穿內褲卻是天下一絕
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.67,0:03:17.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小透 剛才...剛才...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.42,0:03:21.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有想忘穿內褲是天下一絕對吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.12,0:03:23.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小倫！不能跑啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.38,0:03:31.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又來了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.95,0:03:33.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,透 你也夠累的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.55,0:03:36.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起了 透
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.39,0:03:43.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我呢 就是只有早晨比較迷糊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.08,0:03:45.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會睡著了 發呆了之類的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.71,0:03:47.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣的問題嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.32,0:03:49.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她已經穿好了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.15,0:03:54.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這倒也是啊 只是覺得萬一的話...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.19,0:03:57.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了 倫
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.50,0:03:58.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼事？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.98,0:04:03.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天下午的課的筆記 能借我抄一下嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.29,0:04:07.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 你昨天早退來的是吧 行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.96,0:04:08.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.23,0:04:12.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝 得救了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.97,0:04:17.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼語？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.10,0:04:20.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真討厭 日語啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.80,0:04:23.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上課的時候被睡魔襲擊了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.65,0:04:25.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不僅僅是早晨啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.94,0:04:27.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍微有些潦草吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.17,0:04:30.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒 沒這回事啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.04,0:04:33.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.31,0:04:35.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是有看不懂的地方的話要跟我說哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.01,0:04:36.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒？！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.06,0:04:40.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.98,0:04:42.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.43,0:04:45.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,優子 等下也給我看看
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.13,0:04:49.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行啊 抄完了就給倫吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.61,0:04:51.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.72,0:04:58.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個 凪你近視嗎？ 視力大約多少？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.85,0:05:00.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,2.0
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.56,0:05:03.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是平光鏡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.21,0:05:05.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼要戴平光鏡？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.60,0:05:11.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不戴這個的話 不該看的東西也會看到
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.19,0:05:15.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那莫非是...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.40,0:05:20.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 現在就在優子背後
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.00,0:05:23.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛 這是騙你的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.72,0:05:25.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我都說是開玩笑的了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.82,0:05:28.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要 不要啊——
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.67,0:05:31.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還真是好騙呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.07,0:05:33.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是普通的近視而已
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.70,0:05:37.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要這樣啦 我最怕恐怖故事了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.80,0:05:39.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也嚇了一跳
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.92,0:05:42.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小凪的演技好棒
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.34,0:05:44.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都能進演劇部了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.92,0:05:45.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經進了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.72,0:05:47.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然是幽靈部員
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.98,0:05:49.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好棒...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.74,0:05:50.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...才怪
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.90,0:06:02.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在這個夏天從你那收到兩三次信了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.17,0:06:07.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寫著"想在東京得到相當的地位 拜託你了"的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.17,0:06:11.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我記得是第二封信來的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.90,0:06:11.03,*Default,+,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs30}（摘自夏目漱石代表作之一 「心」的“下 先生與遺書”第一段）
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.49,0:06:09.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好想去廁所
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.53,0:06:16.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9\fs30}下一章的“老師”→文章中的“我”\N理清個人主義思想和其倫理觀之間的一條界限\N請思考從“老師”的信中能讀出來的人間的自我和葛藤的意義
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.55,0:06:14.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個 老師
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.13,0:06:15.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.14,0:06:18.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.53,0:06:22.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟糕 "想去廁所"太難為情了說不出口
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.73,0:06:27.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我頭好痛...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.34,0:06:29.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,優子 那是肚子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.92,0:06:31.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊不對 那個...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.48,0:06:33.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師 對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.60,0:06:40.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想去廁所 帶優子去保健室的時候 順帶去一下可以嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.50,0:06:41.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.90,0:06:42.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,倫...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.94,0:06:44.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧 優子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.31,0:06:46.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.55,0:06:52.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉了 倫 真的幫大忙了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.90,0:06:55.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼 我也想去嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.91,0:06:57.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼 倫也去廁所？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.26,0:06:59.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.58,0:07:05.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...是保健室
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.51,0:07:11.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,倫！倫 怎麼了！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.14,0:07:13.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪裡不舒服嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.63,0:07:16.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也不清楚 就是很難受
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.77,0:07:21.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能是中什麼邪了 好想吐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.17,0:07:23.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,廁所嗎 還是去保健室？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.23,0:07:29.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 廁所 廁...to...to...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.72,0:07:32.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了 找小透啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.30,0:07:35.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,優子 不是那樣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.88,0:07:43.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,倫 倫 振作啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.53,0:07:46.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,優子 在嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.48,0:07:48.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小透！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.70,0:07:50.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,倫 一下子失去意識了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.31,0:07:54.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天保健室老師也不在 該怎麼辦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.95,0:07:57.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冷靜點啊 比如聯絡別的老師什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.71,0:07:59.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兩位都安靜一點
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.24,0:08:02.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.91,0:08:10.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是睡眠不足而已
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.96,0:08:26.96,*Default,+,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}請安靜
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.63,0:08:34.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下雨了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.62,0:08:36.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒帶傘
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.77,0:08:39.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是 早上還是晴天來著
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.95,0:08:42.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但只是小雨 用跑的應該沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.24,0:08:44.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等我一下 小透
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.81,0:08:46.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看著哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.45,0:08:55.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近我發覺了 其實我是雨女
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.45,0:08:55.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs30}（雨女 日本民間傳說中的呼喚風雨的妖怪）
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.19,0:08:58.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用死撐了 快點回來
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.61,0:09:03.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全濕了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.17,0:09:05.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真亂來
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.99,0:09:15.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是誰啊 死盯著這邊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.19,0:09:19.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在小倫偏偏還是這個樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.92,0:09:23.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小倫 我們去那邊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.10,0:09:23.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.35,0:09:37.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真好 我選這學校太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.74,0:09:42.24,*Default,+,0000,0000,0000,,合宿參加承諾書請交至各負責老師或山田處。
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.51,0:09:44.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小倫 得快點擦幹
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.57,0:09:47.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.04,0:09:49.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小透 穿上這個
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.54,0:09:52.69,*Default,+,0000,0000,0000,,鏘~~
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.54,0:09:52.69,*Default,+,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}（垃圾袋）
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.98,0:09:55.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣就不需要傘了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.81,0:10:02.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都這年齡了還穿這個太牽強了吧 小學生就另當別論
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.39,0:10:04.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 確實...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.23,0:10:06.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,情侶裝太牽強了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.65,0:10:08.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那其中一個人穿就可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.68,0:10:10.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 重點不在這裡...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.62,0:10:13.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是啥...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.14,0:10:16.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我脫掉好了反正我已經淋濕了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.11,0:10:16.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啥呢...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.51,0:10:18.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.17,0:10:21.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 小凪和優子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.32,0:10:24.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別來這邊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.49,0:10:29.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 我還在想你們在幹什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.55,0:10:32.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小倫你都濕透了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.60,0:10:35.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我家很近 要不要來先把衣服弄乾了再走？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.32,0:10:37.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的？ 謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.55,0:10:39.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但外頭還是...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.69,0:10:44.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道校內有雨女不成？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.93,0:10:48.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,該怎麼辦呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.16,0:10:51.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然是豪雨 跑過去就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.37,0:10:55.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起遭殃就不怕啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.02,0:10:59.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛 要是到小凪家的話
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.30,0:11:00.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是懊糟
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.52,0:11:03.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不想被淋所以還是叫計程車吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.33,0:11:06.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這哪是高中生該幹的事情啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.70,0:11:11.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一段時間會不會晴起來呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.75,0:11:12.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看似沒戲
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.99,0:11:14.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以還是叫計程車吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.85,0:11:17.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小凪家是往這邊走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.58,0:11:18.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.59,0:11:19.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 我也要...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.19,0:11:22.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫你等等啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.55,0:11:23.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來啊來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.47,0:11:26.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 別落下我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.76,0:11:31.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雨天明明會讓心情憂鬱 但她們依舊那麼開心
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.67,0:11:35.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,青春啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.28,0:11:45.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有靈感了 有靈感了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.48,0:11:47.03,NETA,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,0)\fs60\pos(246,166)}鬼頭老師
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.07,0:11:47.03,NETA,+,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,0)\pos(184,168)}興趣?詩歌
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.03,0:11:48.82,NETA,+,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(154,394)}詩歌
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.82,0:11:52.03,NETA,+,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(1114,406)}現實
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,---------------------------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.81,0:11:56.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.47,0:11:58.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打擾了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.52,0:11:59.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請進吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.31,0:12:02.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點去洗澡吧 洗澡
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.59,0:12:05.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊咧？兄貴回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.01,0:12:08.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凪 你還有哥哥啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.78,0:12:12.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥 我的朋友們剛剛來了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.13,0:12:15.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,洗手間 不要去用啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.98,0:12:20.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小凪喊你的哥哥叫兄貴的嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.57,0:12:22.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是叫哥哥？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.38,0:12:24.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫兄貴的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.87,0:12:30.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來 因為浴室一次只能進去兩人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.37,0:12:33.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們要分成二組哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.61,0:12:35.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一二 石頭剪刀布
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.73,0:12:39.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 我和小倫先進去了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.22,0:12:43.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走好 那麼我們換身衣服吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.53,0:13:10.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了 仔細想想我還沒有和小透兩人單獨說過話呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.22,0:13:14.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底該怎麼辦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.92,0:13:18.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種時候的沉默有點 有點...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.63,0:13:22.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,優子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.18,0:13:23.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.89,0:13:25.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們放點什麼東西吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.64,0:13:26.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.14,0:13:28.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,DVD 有很多哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.54,0:13:29.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說的也是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.20,0:13:37.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「真實存在的恐怖都市傳說」和保持沉默
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.62,0:13:38.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你選哪個？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.21,0:13:40.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終極的選擇
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.92,0:13:44.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼把衣服放在那邊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.25,0:13:46.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的 是這裡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.53,0:13:49.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼快點進去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.97,0:13:51.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒 你是誰？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.95,0:13:54.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？ 是倫啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.16,0:13:59.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然是知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.95,0:14:05.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過只是放下了劉海 改變還真大呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.87,0:14:13.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是誰？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.35,0:14:16.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那種反應 早就膩了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.23,0:14:24.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是愜意
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.67,0:14:26.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真讓人痛快啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.79,0:14:29.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是得要趁早洗完才行
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.08,0:14:34.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說的也是呢 不快點跟小透和優子醬交換的話
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.18,0:14:38.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在我的房間裡只有她們兩人了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.96,0:14:40.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會有事吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.98,0:14:44.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事的 兩人可是好朋友啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.13,0:14:49.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛 雖說是那樣...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.40,0:15:08.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 不行 這樣下去不行
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.23,0:15:12.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了 把眼睛閉上就不害怕了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.08,0:15:24.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我好想叫出聲來
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.72,0:15:27.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.15,0:15:29.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 快點去洗澡…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.91,0:15:32.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 優子 浴室空了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.68,0:15:34.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,優子～
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.19,0:15:37.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,優子？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.20,0:15:39.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,優子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.20,0:15:43.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,優子？優子 糟了優子她…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.91,0:15:45.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底發生了什麼啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.45,0:15:49.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呀～真是嚇死人了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.59,0:15:53.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終於可以洗澡了 是吧 小透
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.73,0:15:54.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.93,0:15:58.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼進去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.52,0:16:09.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個 透在洗頭髮時有沒有因為看不到前面
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.39,0:16:11.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而感到害怕的時候？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.48,0:16:19.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我小時候非常受不了洗髮水
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.33,0:16:26.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 洗髮水進眼裡去了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.41,0:16:29.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在幹什麼啊 小透
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.18,0:16:31.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,淋浴在什麼地方？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.53,0:16:35.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,眼睛 眼睛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.23,0:16:40.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說優子 太吵了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.01,0:16:42.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要 住手啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.11,0:16:48.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 我都以為快要斷氣了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.66,0:17:04.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 意識變得朦朧了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.29,0:17:09.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,倫 快看啊 看到綠洲了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.55,0:17:12.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凪 倫
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.51,0:17:15.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們兩人在幹什麼啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.38,0:17:21.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,優子　水的溫度怎麼樣啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.58,0:17:23.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起那種事…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.05,0:17:26.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說 把暖氣關掉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.09,0:17:29.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本打算是要弄乾衣服的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.84,0:17:35.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真好喝
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.43,0:17:37.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 活過來了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.30,0:17:39.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是擔心死我了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.31,0:17:42.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差不多幹了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.17,0:17:45.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雨快點停下來就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.91,0:17:48.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暫時還是不行的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.16,0:17:50.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下得真久呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.17,0:17:53.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下雨天的時候就要說到梳理頭髮了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.84,0:17:56.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的頭髮總是黏在一起呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.16,0:17:59.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的頭髮會叉開來完全整理不好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.52,0:18:02.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是因為發質不一樣呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.06,0:18:06.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小優的頭髮讓我摸一下
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.17,0:18:07.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 可以
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.75,0:18:11.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇 優子的頭髮真漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.56,0:18:12.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,透
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.52,0:18:15.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全沒有分叉呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.33,0:18:14.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要玩嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.49,0:18:18.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有那種事哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.08,0:18:39.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那這個衣服很可愛吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.90,0:18:43.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要動 現在正是最關鍵的時刻
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.25,0:18:45.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.52,0:18:47.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好很好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.42,0:18:52.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.06,0:18:54.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能動
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.12,0:19:01.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 我輸了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.80,0:19:04.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還要玩嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.11,0:19:07.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要刷新凪的記錄
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.90,0:19:09.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,性格真不錯呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.23,0:19:16.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,優子的指甲真漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.55,0:19:19.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有那樣的事啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.30,0:19:20.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有做過什麼保養嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.42,0:19:23.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有特別做過什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.45,0:19:25.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 那樣的話
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.60,0:19:36.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然很舒服 總覺得很讓人好害羞呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.76,0:19:42.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小透 等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.49,0:19:45.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要動
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.88,0:19:45.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,定住
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.58,0:19:50.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 要我怎麼做才好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.56,0:20:06.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}雨好像還沒停
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.36,0:20:07.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}下得真久呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.91,0:20:12.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}但是我很喜歡雨聲哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.14,0:20:13.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}誒
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.24,0:20:16.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}啊 稍微有點理解呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.26,0:20:17.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}是吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.69,0:20:21.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}小凪也閉上眼睛聽聽看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.31,0:20:25.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}誒～ 呀 我就…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.88,0:21:22.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,確實 感覺不錯呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.88,0:21:28.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 好像在烤著什麼的聲音呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.57,0:21:31.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像肚子餓了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.16,0:21:33.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小倫
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.92,0:21:37.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 是我的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.65,0:21:38.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又來了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.64,0:21:43.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再見了 回去的時候要當心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.48,0:21:46.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 連傘都借給我太謝謝了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.63,0:21:48.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 明天見
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.12,0:21:50.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打擾了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.23,0:21:53.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再見
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.15,0:21:58.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那 這把傘很可愛呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.08,0:21:59.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說的是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.12,0:22:01.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 雨還是很大啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.40,0:22:03.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下一班電車是幾點來的？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.83,0:22:09.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥 現在洗手間可以用了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.01,0:22:22.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有說過 要當心點了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.88,0:22:23.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,---------------------------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.58,0:23:59.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.31,0:24:02.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集終於柚多穀和美穂要登場了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.32,0:24:03.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.59,0:24:05.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想來還真是漫長啊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.32,0:24:07.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 人生回顧到此為止
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.39,0:24:11.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說我們第一話沒有出現過吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.03,0:24:14.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼說起來的話我們在片頭曲中有出現過啊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.08,0:24:15.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛 說的也是
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.85,0:24:18.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集A Channel 同級生
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.68,0:24:20.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 不只是同級生
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.55,0:24:23.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然上級生的前輩們也會登場哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,---------------------------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.76,0:20:05.26,IN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放課後予定もなんもないし
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.26,0:20:10.10,IN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雨が降ってるから
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.10,0:20:12.73,IN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,うちに集合
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.02,0:20:20.57,IN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,君は普段から素直じゃないけれど
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.57,0:20:24.45,IN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今日はきっと分かるはず
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.45,0:20:30.58,IN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笑顔がみたいだけだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.62,0:20:40.47,IN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,そんな所にかくれないでいいから
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.47,0:20:44.39,IN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,もっとほら近づいて
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.39,0:20:48.06,IN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,きみも友達だよ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.06,0:20:56.15,IN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,これから何度も過ぎでいく季節も
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.15,0:20:59.86,IN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ずっとほら近くにいて
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.86,0:21:05.87,IN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,きみと一緒にいたいよ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.70,0:21:13.71,IN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,きみと笑ってたいんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,---------------------------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.76,0:20:05.26,IN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放課後什麼預定都沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.26,0:20:10.10,IN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為下雨了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.10,0:20:12.73,IN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就到我家來集合吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.02,0:20:20.57,IN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然你平時就不坦率
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.57,0:20:24.45,IN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但今天我一定會了解你的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.45,0:20:30.58,IN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是想看到你的笑臉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.62,0:20:40.47,IN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用藏在那種地方也可以
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.47,0:20:44.39,IN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再靠近一點
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.39,0:20:48.06,IN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也是我的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.06,0:20:56.15,IN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從今以後在更替的四季中
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.15,0:20:59.86,IN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直呆在我的身邊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.86,0:21:05.87,IN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想和你在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.70,0:21:13.71,IN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想和你一起歡笑